trans-unit.source: Represents a single item of data extracted from a workflow and all its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: 워크플로와 연결된 된 모든 주석에서 추출 된 데이터의 단일 항목을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a track point, it sends a tracking record to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]런타임 추적 인프라가 추적 지점을 일치 시킬 때 추적 레코드를 추적 서비스로 보냅니다.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> may contain <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects that specify data to be extracted from the workflow and returned in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> or the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>워크플로에서 추출할 데이터를 지정 하 고 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>나 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> 반환 하는 개체</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> 또는</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> 포함 될 수 있습니다</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: A TrackingDataItem represents a single item of this extracted data in either <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: TrackingDataItem 중 하나 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>나 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 이 추출 된 데이터의 단일 항목을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> class.
Gets and sets the list of annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: 가져오고 추출한 데이터와 연결 된 주석 목록을 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> can specify annotations to be sent with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>또는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>추출한 데이터와 보내야 하는 주석을 지정할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: These are contained in the Annotations property.
A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> 추출한 데이터와 연결 된 주석을 포함 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the extracted data associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 와 연결 된 추출한 데이터를 가져오거나 설정 합니다.는 <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Data contains the member data, specified by an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, that was extracted from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: 지정한 멤버 데이터를 포함 하는 데이터는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>또는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, 워크플로 인스턴스에서 추출한.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that represents the extracted data.
Gets or sets the name of the property or field associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: 추출한 데이터와 연결 된 필드나 속성의 이름을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure supports data extraction on fields and properties of classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; a member of such a field or property; and a single item of a field or a property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface, for example a single element in a collection.
trans-unit.target: 런타임 추적 인프라에서 상속 된 클래스의 필드 및 속성에 데이터 추출을 지원 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>이러한 필드 또는 속성의 멤버 and 구현 하는 필드 또는 속성 (또는 그룹의 멤버)의 단일 항목의 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>인터페이스, 예: 컬렉션의 단일 요소입니다.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: FieldName contains the dot delineated name of the item extracted and is equivalent to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> depending on which type of extract specified the data contained by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.
trans-unit.target: FieldName 추출 된 항목의 점 점으로 구분 된 이름을 포함 하 고 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>지정 된 추출 형식에 따라에 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> 포함 된 데이터</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> 또는</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> 해당 하는

trans-unit.source: The dot delineated name of the property or field that was extracted.
trans-unit.target: 이 점으로 추출 된 필드나 속성의 이름입니다.
